# Keep shell/script files LF-only. A CRLF shebang (e.g. "#!/bin/bash\r") makes a
# script unexecutable ("cannot execute: required file not found") — this broke the
# Spore Plex transcoder wrapper after a Windows-side (Ebony) deploy on 2026-06-21.
*.sh    text eol=lf
*.bash  text eol=lf
*.py    text eol=lf
